OH, YEAH? YOU GOT A WORLD HOCKEY

20:10.501 --> 20:12.628
LEAGUE MEETING TO GET TO?

20:12.628 --> 20:14.213
I'M SORRY, WHAT?

20:14.213 --> 20:16.174
DON'T EMBARRASS YOURSELF

20:14.213 --> 20:16.174
ANY MORE THAN YOU ALREADY HAVE.

20:16.174 --> 20:18.300
I PLAYED HOCKEY IN RUSSIA

20:16.174 --> 20:18.300
FOR TWO YEARS.

20:18.300 --> 20:20.136
YOUR ACCENT IS...

