IS TRUE.

20:21.428 --> 20:22.763
THANKS, VLAD.

20:22.763 --> 20:24.807
I WANT IN.

20:24.807 --> 20:26.350
LOOK, YOU DON'T KNOW

20:24.807 --> 20:26.350
A DAMN THING ABOUT IT.

20:26.350 --> 20:27.601
I KNOW EVERYTHING ABOUT IT.

20:27.601 --> 20:30.146
MY LAWYER JUST SENT IT

20:27.601 --> 20:30.146
TO ME, OKAY?

20:30.146 --> 20:32.314
YOU'RE SCOUTING FOR

20:30.146 --> 20:32.314
THE ONLY AMERICAN FRANCHISE

20:32.314 --> 20:33.900
RIGHT HERE IN OREGON.

20:33.900 --> 20:36.777
PROJECTED REVENUES

20:33.900 --> 20:36.777
IN TENS OF MILLIONS OF DOLLARS.

20:36.777 --> 20:38.445
NO WONDER

20:36.777 --> 20:38.445
A SUPERSTAR LIKE BUSIAK

20:38.445 --> 20:40.239
IS HANGING

20:38.445 --> 20:40.239
WITH A SCRUB LIKE YOU.

20:40.239 --> 20:42.116
YOU'RE PRETTY SCRUBBY.

20:42.116 --> 20:43.409
VLAD, PLEASE.

20:43.409 --> 20:45.912
LISTEN, RISING,

20:43.409 --> 20:45.912
IT'S NOT UP TO ME, OKAY?

20:45.912 --> 20:47.454
HERE'S THE THING.

20:47.454 --> 20:50.041
-YOU -- YOU WOULD

20:47.454 --> 20:50.041
HAVE TO MEET OLYENKOV.

20:47.454 --> 20:50.041
-OLYENKOV?

20:50.041 --> 20:52.585
YEAH. NADIA OLYENKOV.

20:50.041 --> 20:52.585
THIS IS HER SHOW.

20:52.585 --> 20:55.088
OKAY, SHE'S GOT $2 BILLION

20:52.585 --> 20:55.088
OF HER OWN MONEY IN THE WHL.

20:55.088 --> 20:57.673
SHE'S CRAZY, BUT SHE'S RICH.

20:55.088 --> 20:57.673
SHE KNOWS HOW TO MAKE A DEAL.

20:57.673 --> 20:58.966
OKAY, SO INTRODUCE US.

20:58.966 --> 21:01.010
NO, IT'S NOT GONNA --

20:58.966 --> 21:01.010
NOT GONNA WORK.

21:01.010 --> 21:02.636
NO, THERE'S ONLY ONE WAY

21:01.010 --> 21:02.636
SHE LETS PEOPLE IN.

21:02.636 --> 21:04.597
WELL, TELL ME WHAT IT IS,

21:02.636 --> 21:04.597
AND I'LL DO IT.

21:07.016 --> 21:09.351
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO MAKE

21:07.016 --> 21:09.351
FRIENDS WITH THE ZACATO.

21:09.351 --> 21:10.937
WHAT IS THAT, SOME KIND OF CODE?

21:10.937 --> 21:13.106
NO.

21:13.106 --> 21:15.524
COME ON, VLAD.

21:18.611 --> 21:20.238
UH, NADIA, THIS IS PETE RISING.

21:20.238 --> 21:21.614
YOU KNOW, WE DISCUSSED THE D--

21:21.614 --> 21:22.573
[ Russian accent ] NYET.

21:22.573 --> 21:24.283
AH.

21:24.283 --> 21:25.492
NYET. OKAY.

21:24.283 --> 21:25.492
WELL, THAT'S IT.

21:25.492 --> 21:26.702
YOU HAD YOUR SHOT.

21:25.492 --> 21:26.702
LET'S GO.

21:26.702 --> 21:28.037
WHAT? NO!

21:28.037 --> 21:31.373
I'M NOT -- MS. OLYENKOV,

21:28.037 --> 21:31.373
NADIA -- WHATEVER --

21:31.373 --> 21:32.917
I DON'T WANT TO WASTE YOUR TIME.

21:32.917 --> 21:34.460
JUST GIVE ME 30 SECONDS, PLEASE.

21:34.460 --> 21:36.837
[ SIGHS ]

21:38.089 --> 21:39.465
GO.

21:39.465 --> 21:40.758
Okay, go, go.

21:40.758 --> 21:42.384
ALL RIGHT, LOOK.

21:42.384 --> 21:45.304
I OWN A MINOR-LEAGUE TEAM

21:42.384 --> 21:45.304
RIGHT HERE IN TOWN

21:45.304 --> 21:46.764
THAT'S GOOD ENOUGH

21:45.304 --> 21:46.764
FOR THE MAJORS.

21:46.764 --> 21:48.099
BUT I'VE NEVER BUMPED THEM.

21:46.764 --> 21:48.099
YOU KNOW WHY?

21:48.099 --> 21:51.144
POLITICS, CAPITAL INVESTMENT,

21:51.144 --> 21:54.021
MAYBE YOU HAVE SMALL BRAIN.

21:54.021 --> 21:55.231
NO.

21:55.231 --> 21:57.108
IT'S BECAUSE THE NHL

21:55.231 --> 21:57.108
WAS TOO SMALL.

21:57.108 --> 21:58.734
I DIDN'T KNOW IT AT THE TIME,

21:58.734 --> 22:00.527
BUT I WAS WAITING

21:58.734 --> 22:00.527
FOR SOMETHING GLOBAL.

22:00.527 --> 22:02.655
NOW, YOU NEED

22:00.527 --> 22:02.655
AN AMERICAN HOCKEY TEAM

22:02.655 --> 22:04.949
FOR THE WORLD HOCKEY LEAGUE,

22:02.655 --> 22:04.949
OKAY?

22:04.949 --> 22:07.493
YOU'RE OBVIOUSLY

22:04.949 --> 22:07.493
NOT INTERESTED IN THE NHL,

22:07.493 --> 22:09.078
OR YOU WOULDN'T BE HERE.

22:09.078 --> 22:10.788
INSTEAD OF SPENDING FIVE YEARS

22:10.788 --> 22:12.999
BUILDING A STADIUM

22:10.788 --> 22:12.999
AND CREATING A TEAM,

22:12.999 --> 22:14.959
WHY NOT TAKE

22:12.999 --> 22:14.959
WHAT'S ALREADY HERE?

22:14.959 --> 22:16.752
YOU'LL LOVE THE OTTERS.

22:16.752 --> 22:21.757
YOU THINK OTTERS

22:16.752 --> 22:21.757
HIT MY SWEET SPOT?

22:21.757 --> 22:25.343
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

22:27.180 --> 22:30.474
NO, NO, NO. SHE'S TALKING

22:27.180 --> 22:30.474
TO THE ZACATO. YEAH.

22:30.474 --> 22:33.686
YEAH. THERE'S ONLY THREE IN

22:30.474 --> 22:33.686
THE WORLD. THAT'S ONE OF THEM.

22:33.686 --> 22:35.479
HMM.

22:35.479 --> 22:37.982
I THINK HE LIKES YOU.

22:37.982 --> 22:43.196
YEAH? WELL, I LIKE...IT?

22:43.196 --> 22:44.738
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:44.738 --> 22:45.865
[ CLICKS TONGUE ] NO.

22:45.865 --> 22:47.533
NO, NO.

22:45.865 --> 22:47.533
DON'T WANT TO DO THAT.

22:47.533 --> 22:49.535
HE'LL GO RIGHT THROUGH

22:47.533 --> 22:49.535
THE GLASS, TAKE YOUR HAND OFF.

22:49.535 --> 22:51.162
OKAY.

22:51.162 --> 22:53.080
NO.

22:53.080 --> 22:57.084
TOMORROW, YOU BRING ME $500,000.

22:57.084 --> 22:58.336
THEN YOU JOIN.

22:58.336 --> 23:00.420
YOU GOT IT.

23:01.630 --> 23:05.509
THERE WE GO. FANTASTIC.

23:16.979 --> 23:20.107
GREAT PRACTICE, JACQUES!

23:20.107 --> 23:23.069
IT'S "JACK."

23:23.069 --> 23:24.737
[ GRUNTS ]

23:29.116 --> 23:31.618
MARKO, I AIN'T

23:29.116 --> 23:31.618
PLAYING WITH YOU, MAN.

23:34.830 --> 23:36.290
I'M NOT GONNA FIGHT YOU, CRAIG!

23:36.290 --> 23:39.293
YOU'RE NOT GONNA HAVE A CHOICE!

23:40.294 --> 23:42.462
YOU KNOW WHAT YOUR

23:40.294 --> 23:42.462
L4 AND YOUR L5 IS?!

23:42.462 --> 23:44.631
IT'S YOUR LOWER VERTEBRAE

23:42.462 --> 23:44.631
ON YOUR SPINE!

23:44.631 --> 23:46.050
YOURS IS CRACKED ALL TO HELL.

23:46.050 --> 23:48.261
ONE SHOT TO IT

23:46.050 --> 23:48.261
AND YOU DON'T WALK AGAIN.

23:48.261 --> 23:49.970
YOU THINK YOU KNOW EVERYTHING

23:48.261 --> 23:49.970
ABOUT ME, DON'T YOU?

23:49.970 --> 23:52.139
I KNOW YOU GOT EDEMA

23:49.970 --> 23:52.139
IN YOUR BRAIN!

23:53.057 --> 23:54.600
I KNOW YOU GOT

23:53.057 --> 23:54.600
AN ENLARGED HEART.

23:54.600 --> 23:56.727
-YOU WANT ME TO KEEP GOING?

23:54.600 --> 23:56.727
-NOT REALLY.

23:56.727 --> 23:58.062
NO.

23:58.062 --> 24:00.731
I'M GONNA TELL YOU

23:58.062 --> 24:00.731
WHAT I KNOW ABOUT YOU.

24:00.731 --> 24:02.066
I KNOW YOU DON'T HAVE A KID,

24:02.066 --> 24:03.525
'CAUSE YOU JUST TRIED

24:02.066 --> 24:03.525
YOUR DEAD-LEVEL BEST

24:03.525 --> 24:05.194
TO SCARE THE HELL OUT OF ME,

24:05.194 --> 24:06.987
AND YOU DIDN'T MENTION

24:05.194 --> 24:06.987
MY SON ONCE.

24:06.987 --> 24:11.575
SO I DON'T CARE ABOUT ALL

24:06.987 --> 24:11.575
THE X-RAYS AND MRIs YOU'VE SEEN,

24:11.575 --> 24:14.703
'CAUSE YOU DON'T KNOW

24:11.575 --> 24:14.703
A DAMN THING ABOUT ME!

24:17.539 --> 24:20.334
I DO IT FOR MY SON.

24:20.334 --> 24:22.795
THAT'S WHY I SUIT UP.

24:22.795 --> 24:25.589
ONE MORE GAME.

24:25.589 --> 24:28.466
AFTER THAT, I DON'T...

24:28.466 --> 24:31.178
I DON'T CARE WHAT HAPPENS TO ME.

24:31.178 --> 24:33.806
BUT UNTIL YOU HAVE A FAMILY,

24:33.806 --> 24:36.434
I WOULD NEVER EXPECT YOU

24:33.806 --> 24:36.434
TO UNDERSTAND.

24:36.434 --> 24:37.517
[ SIGHS ]

24:37.517 --> 24:38.685
YEAH, YOU'RE RIGHT.

24:40.604 --> 24:42.440
I GOT NO FAMILY.

24:42.440 --> 24:44.691
NOT LIKE YOU MEAN.

24:46.193 --> 24:48.528
BUT I HAD BROTHERS.

24:48.528 --> 24:50.406
I HAD A LOT OF 'EM.

24:50.406 --> 24:52.408
I DIDN'T KNOW ALL THEIR NAMES --

24:50.406 --> 24:52.408
NOT ALL OF 'EM --

24:52.408 --> 24:54.285
BUT I KNEW THEIR FACES,

24:54.285 --> 24:56.829
AND I KNEW THEIR RANK.

24:56.829 --> 24:59.123
AND I DID THINGS

24:56.829 --> 24:59.123
THAT I DIDN'T WANT TO DO

24:59.123 --> 25:03.002
BECAUSE THEY COUNTED ON ME --

24:59.123 --> 25:03.002
BAD THINGS FOR GOOD REASONS.

25:03.002 --> 25:05.045
AND YOU KNOW WHAT I LEARNED?

25:05.045 --> 25:07.089
BAD CHOICES ARE BAD CHOICES.

25:07.089 --> 25:09.842
DOESN'T MATTER

25:07.089 --> 25:09.842
WHY YOU MADE THEM.

25:09.842 --> 25:13.595
AND THEY TEAR YOU APART

25:09.842 --> 25:13.595
FROM THE INSIDE OUT.

25:13.595 --> 25:16.390
AND YOU DON'T EVEN NOTICE.

25:25.816 --> 25:29.069
HE'S PUTTING BOUNTIES

25:25.816 --> 25:29.069
OUT ON YOU, CRAIG!

25:29.069 --> 25:32.198
RISING'S PAYING PEOPLE

25:29.069 --> 25:32.198
TO TAKE YOU OUT!

25:33.240 --> 25:36.369
GOOD LUCK FINDING THE GUY

25:33.240 --> 25:36.369
THAT CAN DO THAT.

25:46.670 --> 25:48.464
[ SIGHS ]

25:48.464 --> 25:50.132
DID I FALL ASLEEP AGAIN?

25:50.132 --> 25:51.050
YEAH.

25:51.050 --> 25:53.177
THANKS.

25:51.050 --> 25:53.177
[ SNIFFLES ]

25:53.177 --> 25:55.679
HOW DID THE MOVIE END?

25:55.679 --> 25:57.931
SOYLENT GREEN IS PEOPLE.

25:57.931 --> 25:59.725
-WHOA.

25:57.931 --> 25:59.725
-I KNOW.

25:59.725 --> 26:01.101
JUST SIT WITH IT FOR A WHILE.

26:01.101 --> 26:02.186
YUCK.

26:02.186 --> 26:04.522
WHAT'S UP?

26:04.522 --> 26:07.525
THERE'S SOMETHING WEIRD

26:04.522 --> 26:07.525
IN RISING'S FINANCIALS.

26:07.525 --> 26:10.319
UH, YOU SHOULD GET CHANGED.

26:07.525 --> 26:10.319
IT'S TIME TO GO MEET NATE.

26:10.319 --> 26:11.487
OKAY.

26:17.617 --> 26:21.121
ARE YOU HAVING

26:17.617 --> 26:21.121
A STARING CONTEST WITH A TURTLE?

26:21.121 --> 26:24.250
NO, I JUST WON

26:21.121 --> 26:24.250
A STARING CONTEST WITH A TURTLE.

26:24.250 --> 26:28.670
IS IT WEIRD THAT I FIND THAT

26:24.250 --> 26:28.670
ODDLY ATTRACTIVE?

26:28.670 --> 26:31.798
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

26:33.050 --> 26:34.801
SO, DID YOU WIN?

26:34.801 --> 26:36.095
DID I WHAT?

26:36.095 --> 26:38.514
CONTEST.

26:38.514 --> 26:40.598
OH, YES.

26:38.514 --> 26:40.598
YES, I DID. YES.

26:40.598 --> 26:42.351
VLAD, WOULD YOU MIND

26:40.598 --> 26:42.351
GRABBING THE DOOR?

26:42.351 --> 26:43.643
OUR GUEST IS HERE.

26:49.358 --> 26:50.608
PETE. COME IN.

26:50.608 --> 26:51.860
HOW YOU DOING?

26:51.860 --> 26:54.321
GOOD. HOW ARE YOU?

26:56.240 --> 26:57.783
HERE'S THE THING.

26:57.783 --> 27:00.286
YOU GUYS ARE FOR REAL.

27:00.286 --> 27:03.956
YOU GOT THE BEST MARKETING

27:00.286 --> 27:03.956
FIRMS, BILLIONS IN BACKING.

27:03.956 --> 27:06.250
AND I KNOW ENOUGH

27:03.956 --> 27:06.250
ABOUT THIS BUSINESS

27:06.250 --> 27:09.211
TO KNOW THAT

27:06.250 --> 27:09.211
IN A DEAL LIKE THIS,

27:09.211 --> 27:12.256
SOONER OR LATER,

27:09.211 --> 27:12.256
YOU GUYS WILL SQUEEZE ME OUT.

27:12.256 --> 27:16.218
I ALSO KNOW ENOUGH TO RECOGNIZE

27:12.256 --> 27:16.218
WHEN I CAN'T COMPETE, SO...

27:16.218 --> 27:17.470
I'M OUT.

27:18.262 --> 27:20.055
[ Russian accent ]

27:18.262 --> 27:20.055
OUT OF WHL?

27:20.055 --> 27:21.639
OUT OF HOCKEY.

27:21.639 --> 27:24.310
MY TEAM'S BANKRUPT.

27:21.639 --> 27:24.310
I'M FILING ON MONDAY.

27:24.310 --> 27:26.437
SO, IF YOU WANT

27:24.310 --> 27:26.437
TO BUY THIS FRANCHISE,

27:26.437 --> 27:28.481
YOU HAVE TO BE FIRST IN LINE.

27:28.481 --> 27:31.275
OF COURSE, THE BANK WILL WANT

27:28.481 --> 27:31.275
YOU TO PAY OFF THE $5 MILLION.

27:31.275 --> 27:32.859
WHAT $5 MILLION?

27:32.859 --> 27:34.736
THERE'S A LOT OF UNPAID BILLS,

27:34.736 --> 27:36.113
AND I HAVEN'T TAKEN

27:34.736 --> 27:36.113
A SALARY MYSELF

27:36.113 --> 27:37.364
FOR QUITE SOME TIME, SO...

27:37.364 --> 27:40.159
HOW MUCH OF THAT

27:37.364 --> 27:40.159
IS YOUR DEFERRED SALARY?

27:40.159 --> 27:43.078
$4 MILLION.

27:43.996 --> 27:45.956
SO, HEY, GOOD LUCK WITH IT ALL.

27:45.956 --> 27:48.875
MAYBE I'LL SEE YOU

27:45.956 --> 27:48.875
ON THE ICE AGAIN SOMEDAY, HUH?

27:53.422 --> 27:56.258
[ SIGHS ]

27:53.422 --> 27:56.258
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

27:56.258 --> 27:57.510
[ SIGHS ]

27:57.510 --> 27:59.595
WHAT THE HELL JUST HAPPENED?

27:59.595 --> 28:01.805
YOU DID TOO GOOD A JOB.

28:01.805 --> 28:03.807
THANKS, VLAD.

28:06.352 --> 28:07.853
OKAY, NOT ONLY

28:06.352 --> 28:07.853
DID HE NOT BRING ANY MONEY,

28:07.853 --> 28:09.813
BUT SOMEONE --

28:07.853 --> 28:09.813
I WON'T MENTION ANY NAMES --

28:09.813 --> 28:12.107
WENT A LITTLE OVERBOARD

28:09.813 --> 28:12.107
IN THE WHL MARKETING MATERIALS.

28:12.107 --> 28:14.193
WHAT? LIKE I'M SUPPOSED TO DO

28:12.107 --> 28:14.193
A BAD JOB?

28:14.193 --> 28:16.069
WELL, NO,

28:14.193 --> 28:16.069
BUT YOU DID SUCH A GOOD JOB

28:16.069 --> 28:18.030
THAT HE DECIDED

28:16.069 --> 28:18.030
TO DECLARE BANKRUPTCY

28:18.030 --> 28:20.073
-RATHER THAN COMPETE.

28:18.030 --> 28:20.073
-AND WHAT ABOUT MARKO'S BONUS?

28:20.073 --> 28:21.783
YEAH, MARKO'S BONUS.

28:20.073 --> 28:21.783
WELL, FORGET ABOUT THAT.

28:21.783 --> 28:23.701
I MEAN, WE PRETTY MUCH ENSURED

28:21.783 --> 28:23.701
THAT MARKO'S BONUS

28:23.701 --> 28:25.204
AND THE REST

28:23.701 --> 28:25.204
OF THE TEAM'S BONUS,

28:25.204 --> 28:26.788
SALARY, INSURANCE -- GONE.

28:26.788 --> 28:28.332
YESTERDAY HE ACCESSED AN ACCOUNT

28:28.332 --> 28:30.209
THAT WAS HELD BY A SHELL COMPANY

28:28.332 --> 28:30.209
WITH A CHAIN OF TITLE

28:30.209 --> 28:31.877
SO CONVOLUTED

28:30.209 --> 28:31.877
I'M STILL UNRAVELING IT.

28:31.877 --> 28:33.295
HE CLEANED EVERYTHING OUT.

28:33.295 --> 28:35.297
OKAY. HE'S SKIMMING

28:33.295 --> 28:35.297
FROM THE TEAM. YEAH.

28:35.297 --> 28:37.508
HE SAID THAT MOST YEARS,

28:35.297 --> 28:37.508
HE LOSES MONEY ON THE TEAM,

28:37.508 --> 28:40.135
BUT THE TEAM'S ACTUALLY

28:37.508 --> 28:40.135
DOING PRETTY SOLID BUSINESS.

28:40.135 --> 28:42.304
YEP. HE'S STEALING

28:40.135 --> 28:42.304
FROM THE OPERATION.

28:42.304 --> 28:44.348
YEAH, AND THAT'S WHY

28:42.304 --> 28:44.348
HE'S AFRAID OF US,

28:44.348 --> 28:46.350
BECAUSE IF WE INVITE HIM

28:44.348 --> 28:46.350
INTO THE FRANCHISE,

28:46.350 --> 28:48.768
THERE'S GONNA BE AN AUDIT

28:46.350 --> 28:48.768
TO END ALL AUDITS.

28:48.768 --> 28:51.564
WHO'S HUNGRY?

28:48.768 --> 28:51.564
HEY, ANYBODY, DOUGHNUTS?

28:51.564 --> 28:54.483
BUT WHA-- HOW COME HE HASN'T

28:51.564 --> 28:54.483
SPENT ANY OF THE MONEY?

28:54.483 --> 28:56.235
HE HAS NO WAY TO HIDE IT

28:54.483 --> 28:56.235
FROM THE GOVERNMENT.

28:56.235 --> 28:58.362
WELL, HOW DOES THAT CHANGE

28:56.235 --> 28:58.362
AFTER HE DECLARES BANKRUPTCY?

28:58.362 --> 28:59.697
IT DOESN'T.

28:59.697 --> 29:01.615
RISING IS GOING TO LAUNDER

28:59.697 --> 29:01.615
MONEY, YEAH?

29:01.615 --> 29:03.617
YEAH. YEAH, THAT'S GREAT.

29:01.615 --> 29:03.617
THANKS. THANKS, THERE, VLAD.

29:03.617 --> 29:05.118
THE QUESTION IS WHEN?

29:05.118 --> 29:06.745
-TONIGHT.

29:05.118 --> 29:06.745
-TONIGHT?

29:06.745 --> 29:08.205
YOU THINK YOU CAN

29:06.745 --> 29:08.205
COME UP WITH A PLAN?

29:08.205 --> 29:09.373
ALREADY HAVE. IT'S IN

29:08.205 --> 29:09.373
ONE OF MY CONTINGENCIES.

29:09.373 --> 29:10.666
OKAY.

29:09.373 --> 29:10.666
I WANT TO HEAR THIS PLAN.

29:10.666 --> 29:12.585
HARDISON,

29:10.666 --> 29:12.585
YOU'RE GONNA BE WITH SOPHIE.

29:12.585 --> 29:14.670
WE WERE NEVER HERE IN THIS

29:12.585 --> 29:14.670
APARTMENT. IT DIDN'T EXIST.

29:14.670 --> 29:16.380
VLAD, THANK YOU

29:14.670 --> 29:16.380
FOR THE AUTOGRAPHED STICK,

29:16.380 --> 29:17.839
PUCK, AND GLOVES.

29:19.425 --> 29:20.842
ANY TIME.

29:20.842 --> 29:23.470
THANK YOU.

29:24.430 --> 29:26.181
[ WHISTLE BLOWS ]

29:26.181 --> 29:27.641
ONE GAME LEFT, BOYS.

29:27.641 --> 29:29.602
WE GOT TO LEAVE IT ALL

29:27.641 --> 29:29.602
ON THE ICE TONIGHT.

29:29.602 --> 29:30.936
HUSTLE UP!

29:30.936 --> 29:33.105
THE SKATE --

29:30.936 --> 29:33.105
KNEE WENT RIGHT THROUGH IT.

29:34.398 --> 29:37.359
KEEP IT GOING!

29:37.359 --> 29:38.444
-HERE YOU GO.

29:37.359 --> 29:38.444
-THANKS.

29:38.444 --> 29:40.529
ENJOY THE GAME.

29:40.529 --> 29:43.115
OKAY, PARKER,

29:40.529 --> 29:43.115
HOW WOULD YOU DO IT?

29:43.115 --> 29:44.700
CASH FLOW STARTS THERE.

29:44.700 --> 29:46.535
-HERE YOU GO.

29:44.700 --> 29:46.535
-THANKS.

29:46.535 --> 29:47.953
EVERY 20 MINUTES, A GUARD

29:47.953 --> 29:50.456
REMOVES THE COLLECTED CASH

29:47.953 --> 29:50.456
FROM THE BOX OFFICE.

29:50.456 --> 29:52.874
AND THE GUARD CARRIES THE CASH

29:50.456 --> 29:52.874
TO RISING'S OFFICE.

