29:55.335 --> 29:57.254
BUT ONLY A BANK OFFICIAL

29:57.254 --> 29:58.838
CAN OPEN ONE UP

29:57.254 --> 29:58.838
TO TAKE THINGS OUT.

29:58.838 --> 30:00.340
IT'S LIKE A MAILBOX

29:58.838 --> 30:00.340
YOU CAN CARRY.

30:00.340 --> 30:01.634
AND THAT IS WHERE RISING

30:01.634 --> 30:03.469
WILL ADD THE EXTRA CASH

30:01.634 --> 30:03.469
TO THE LOCKBOX.

30:03.469 --> 30:05.596
AS LONG AS NO ONE LOOKS TOO

30:03.469 --> 30:05.596
CLOSELY, THEY'LL NEVER KNOW

30:05.596 --> 30:07.598
THAT IT DIDN'T COME

30:05.596 --> 30:07.598
FROM LEGITIMATE TICKET SALES.

30:07.598 --> 30:08.932
IT'S CLASSIC MONEY LAUNDERING.

30:08.932 --> 30:10.434
ONCE THE BOX OFFICE IS CLOSED,

30:10.434 --> 30:12.102
THE LOCKBOX IS CARRIED

30:10.434 --> 30:12.102
FROM RISING'S OFFICE

30:12.102 --> 30:13.687
TO A LOADING ZONE.

30:13.687 --> 30:16.356
AN ARMORED CAR PICKS IT UP,

30:13.687 --> 30:16.356
TAKES IT TO THE BANK.

30:16.356 --> 30:18.484
BUT WE DON'T WANT TO HIT IT

30:16.356 --> 30:18.484
IN RISING'S OFFICE --

30:18.484 --> 30:19.735
TOO MUCH ATTENTION.

30:19.735 --> 30:21.654
AND ONCE THE BOX

30:19.735 --> 30:21.654
IS ON THE ARMORED CAR,

30:21.654 --> 30:23.322
THE BANK'S INSURANCE

30:21.654 --> 30:23.322
KICKS IN,

30:23.322 --> 30:25.699
AND RISING'S

30:23.322 --> 30:25.699
PROTECTED AGAINST THEFT.

30:25.699 --> 30:28.327
SO, THAT JUST LEAVES

30:25.699 --> 30:28.327
ONE PLACE.

30:28.327 --> 30:30.537
MM-HMM.

30:33.081 --> 30:36.376
THIS GUY -- YOUR NEW PARTNER.

30:36.376 --> 30:37.503
YES?

30:37.503 --> 30:39.171
YOU LIKE HIM?

30:39.171 --> 30:42.424
YES.

30:43.925 --> 30:45.552
I LIKE HIM, TOO.

30:52.476 --> 30:54.311
[ SPEAKS RUSSIAN ]

30:57.147 --> 30:59.107
IT'S ALL OR NOTHING TONIGHT,

30:57.147 --> 30:59.107
FOLKS.

30:59.107 --> 31:00.651
GAME SEVEN

30:59.107 --> 31:00.651
HERE IN OTTER TOWN

31:00.651 --> 31:03.821
BETWEEN THE RENO FREEZE

31:00.651 --> 31:03.821
AND YOUR OREGON OTTERS.

31:03.821 --> 31:06.824
THE OTTERS HAVE A NEW HERO

31:03.821 --> 31:06.824
IN JACQUES LaBERT,

31:06.824 --> 31:08.575
THE KID FROM SASKATOON,

31:08.575 --> 31:11.704
WHO'S PROVING HE'S GOT AS MUCH

31:08.575 --> 31:11.704
PUNCH AS CRAIG MARKO.

31:11.704 --> 31:13.330
THE PUCK'S ABOUT TO DROP.

31:13.330 --> 31:15.207
AND HERE WE GO.

31:15.207 --> 31:16.583
[ GRUNTS ]

31:16.583 --> 31:19.002
THE PUCK IS DEFLECTED

31:16.583 --> 31:19.002
BY RAYMONDJACK,

31:19.002 --> 31:21.338
AND THE FREEZE

31:19.002 --> 31:21.338
TAKE EARLY CONTROL.

31:21.338 --> 31:23.465
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

31:25.676 --> 31:29.388
MARKO LOOKS LIKE A SHARK

31:25.676 --> 31:29.388
WITH BLOOD IN THE WATER.

31:30.055 --> 31:32.098
SOMEBODY CALL A DOCTOR.

31:32.098 --> 31:34.560
THERE'S LaBERT AGAIN USING

31:32.098 --> 31:34.560
FRANCO LIKE HE'S A TOBOGGAN.

31:47.489 --> 31:50.992
LaBERT IS

31:47.489 --> 31:50.992
A MAN POSSESSED TONIGHT,

31:50.992 --> 31:54.120
AND HE'S JAWING AT EVERY FREEZE

31:50.992 --> 31:54.120
PLAYER HE MAKES CONTACT WITH.

31:54.120 --> 31:55.497
[ WHISTLE BLOWS ]

31:54.120 --> 31:55.497
LET'S FACE IT OFF.

31:55.497 --> 31:58.291
[ CROWD CHEERING ]

32:01.420 --> 32:03.630
COME ON, DUFFY!

32:03.630 --> 32:05.549
DOWNEY AND MARKO

32:03.630 --> 32:05.549
READY FOR THE FACE-OFF.

32:05.549 --> 32:08.176
PUCK CONTROLLED BY THE OTTERS.

32:05.549 --> 32:08.176
NO, IT'S STOLEN BY VEACH.

32:14.974 --> 32:17.477
LaBERT

32:14.974 --> 32:17.477
IS ALL OVER THE ICE TONIGHT.

32:17.477 --> 32:19.104
HE PINS SIEGEL

32:17.477 --> 32:19.104
AGAINST THE BOARDS

32:19.104 --> 32:21.231
AND IS TALKING TRASH AGAIN.

32:21.231 --> 32:23.149
OH, DOCTOR!

32:23.149 --> 32:24.526
WRONG TEAM!

32:24.526 --> 32:26.612
-I TOLD YOU HOW THIS WOULD GO.

32:24.526 --> 32:26.612
-REMIND ME!

32:26.612 --> 32:29.907
-I JUST DID.

32:26.612 --> 32:29.907
-DID YOU SEE THAT?

32:33.660 --> 32:37.372
HARDISON, I NEED YOU

32:33.660 --> 32:37.372
ON YOUR WAY. NOW.

32:45.297 --> 32:51.094
ONLY 6 1/2 MINUTES LEFT,

32:45.297 --> 32:51.094
AND THE GAME IS STILL TIED.

32:51.094 --> 32:52.095
[ CROWD CHEERING ]

32:52.095 --> 32:53.597
LOOK AT JACK THE BEAR.

32:53.597 --> 32:55.056
EVEN IN THE PENALTY BOX,

32:55.056 --> 32:57.058
HE IS STILL JAWING

32:55.056 --> 32:57.058
AT THE FREEZE PLAYERS.

33:22.083 --> 33:26.379
-SHE'S ALL YOURS.

33:22.083 --> 33:26.379
-THANK YOU, SIR.

33:26.379 --> 33:29.215
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATION ]

33:45.440 --> 33:47.651
LaBERT LAYS A DEVASTATING

33:45.440 --> 33:47.651
CROSS-CHECK ON SCHUCKERSAND...

33:47.651 --> 33:50.487
[ WHISTLE BLOWS ]

33:47.651 --> 33:50.487
THAT'S IT, LaBERT.

33:50.487 --> 33:51.864
I TOLD YOU EVERY TIME, DIDN'T I?

33:51.864 --> 33:52.948
-BACK TO THE BOX.

33:51.864 --> 33:52.948
-TOLD YA.

33:52.948 --> 33:55.450
[ CROWD CHEERING ]

33:59.955 --> 34:02.040
BOY, MARV,

33:59.955 --> 34:02.040
WITH LaBERT IN THE BOX,

34:02.040 --> 34:04.292
MAYBE WE'LL FINALLY

34:02.040 --> 34:04.292
SEE MARKO DO BATTLE.

34:04.292 --> 34:06.628
HERE WE GO, STU.

34:06.628 --> 34:08.380
[ CROWD CHEERING ]

34:15.220 --> 34:17.222
WITH LaBERT STILL WATCHING

34:15.220 --> 34:17.222
FROM THE PENALTY BOX,

34:17.222 --> 34:21.142
THE FREEZE ENJOY 30 MORE SECONDS

34:17.222 --> 34:21.142
OF POWER PLAY.

34:21.142 --> 34:23.228
MARKO'S GOT THAT LOOK

34:21.142 --> 34:23.228
IN HIS EYE, STU.

34:23.228 --> 34:26.231
HE WANTS A GAME-SEVEN SCRUM

34:23.228 --> 34:26.231
WITH SOMEBODY.

34:34.322 --> 34:37.659
CRAIG MARKO HAS BARELY GOTTEN

34:34.322 --> 34:37.659
INTO IT WITH ANYONE

34:37.659 --> 34:38.952
THESE LAST TWO GAMES.

34:38.952 --> 34:40.954
-COME ON.

34:38.952 --> 34:40.954
-SO HE'S ITCHING TO BRAWL.

34:40.954 --> 34:43.122
FIGHT!

34:43.122 --> 34:46.001
DROP YOUR GLOVES!

34:46.001 --> 34:48.127
THIS IS THE MOST AMAZING THING

34:46.001 --> 34:48.127
I'VE EVER SEEN.

34:48.127 --> 34:51.882
THIS GAME HAS COME

34:48.127 --> 34:51.882
TO A COMPLETE STOP.

34:51.882 --> 34:54.009
SOMEBODY FIGHT ME!

34:55.677 --> 34:58.972
LET'S GO!

34:55.677 --> 34:58.972
DROP YOUR GLOVES!

34:58.972 --> 35:01.600
COME ON! LET'S GO!

35:01.600 --> 35:05.478
EVERY DOCTOR HE'S SEEN

35:01.600 --> 35:05.478
HAS SAID THE SAME THING.

35:08.982 --> 35:10.859
YOU DON'T WANT TO BE THE ONE

35:08.982 --> 35:10.859
THAT KILLS A LEGEND, DO YOU?

35:10.859 --> 35:12.652
I'M TRYING TO MAKE YOU SEE

35:12.652 --> 35:14.654
THAT IF YOU HIT HIM

35:12.652 --> 35:14.654
IN THE HEAD ONE MORE TIME,

35:14.654 --> 35:16.322
COULD BE THE LAST ONE.

35:16.322 --> 35:18.867
HE COULD DIE.

35:16.322 --> 35:18.867
EH?

35:20.326 --> 35:22.704
SOMEBODY FIGHT ME!

35:22.704 --> 35:24.748
LET'S GO!

35:27.250 --> 35:29.628
[ PANTING ]

35:29.628 --> 35:32.798
[ CROWD MURMURING ]

36:09.042 --> 36:12.004
[ SIGHS ]

36:28.269 --> 36:31.690
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

36:31.690 --> 36:34.651
LET'S PLAY SOME HOCKEY.

36:34.651 --> 36:37.570
GO!

36:34.651 --> 36:37.570
[ CROWD CHEERING ]

36:37.570 --> 36:39.405
WELL, STU, LOOKS LIKE

36:37.570 --> 36:39.405
WE'RE FINALLY GONNA SEE

36:39.405 --> 36:41.116
MARKO PLAY

36:39.405 --> 36:41.116
THE KIND OF HOCKEY HE DID

36:41.116 --> 36:42.993
BACK IN THE JUNIORS.

36:45.495 --> 36:47.080
[ GRUNTING ]

36:51.292 --> 36:54.295
WE HAVE A PROBLEM.

36:51.292 --> 36:54.295
WE NEED A BANK OFFICIAL ON SITE.

36:56.339 --> 36:58.133
DOWNEY DIGGING IN THE CORNER,

36:58.133 --> 37:00.052
AND THE OTTERS

36:58.133 --> 37:00.052
CONTROL THE PUCK.

37:00.052 --> 37:01.553
IF NOBODY SCORES

37:00.052 --> 37:01.553
IN THE NEXT MINUTE,

37:01.553 --> 37:04.556
WE ARE GOING INTO OVERTIME.

37:06.975 --> 37:08.685
SIR, IT'S STUCK.

37:06.975 --> 37:08.685
WE CAN'T LIFT IT.

37:08.685 --> 37:10.436
SEE?

37:10.436 --> 37:12.397
CAN YOU OPEN IT?

37:17.443 --> 37:19.112
WHAT?

37:40.425 --> 37:42.928
[ CHUCKLES ]

37:42.928 --> 37:44.637
FINAL SECONDS HERE

37:44.637 --> 37:46.806
AS THE OTTERS DRIVE IT

37:44.637 --> 37:46.806
INTO THE CREASE.

37:46.806 --> 37:51.061
WADDELL FLIPS IT TO MARKO,

37:46.806 --> 37:51.061
AND HE SCORES!

37:51.061 --> 37:54.064
HOLY COW! WHAT A SHOT!

37:54.064 --> 37:56.733
[ BUZZER ]

37:54.064 --> 37:56.733
OTTERS WIN! OTTERS WIN!

37:56.733 --> 37:59.819
THAT'S THE END OF THE SEASON

37:56.733 --> 37:59.819
AND THE END OF...

38:10.872 --> 38:13.250
NICE SHOT.

38:18.004 --> 38:20.799
-YOU HERE TO GLOAT?

38:18.004 --> 38:20.799
-A LITTLE.

38:20.799 --> 38:23.676
YOU REALLY GOT ME PINNED UP

38:20.799 --> 38:23.676
AGAINST THE BOARDS.

38:23.676 --> 38:25.553
CAN'T GO TO THE COPS, CAN I?

38:25.553 --> 38:27.847
NO, NOT REALLY.

38:27.847 --> 38:29.975
I'M GONNA LOSE EVERYTHING.

38:29.975 --> 38:33.686
YEAH.

38:29.975 --> 38:33.686
THAT'S SORT OF THE POINT.

38:37.649 --> 38:39.317
WHY?

38:42.445 --> 38:45.157
YOU PUT A BOUNTY OUT

38:42.445 --> 38:45.157
ON YOUR OWN MAN --

38:45.157 --> 38:46.491
A GUY THAT YOU KNEW

38:46.491 --> 38:49.327
PUT HIS LIFE ON THE LINE

38:46.491 --> 38:49.327
FOR HIS TEAMMATES

38:49.327 --> 38:52.371
EVERY TIME

38:49.327 --> 38:52.371
HE STEPPED OUT ONTO THE ICE.

39:06.970 --> 39:10.265
-WHAT'S THIS?

39:06.970 --> 39:10.265
-WHAT IS THIS?

39:10.265 --> 39:12.558
I THINK THEY MAY HAVE FOUND OUT

39:10.265 --> 39:12.558
ABOUT YOUR LITTLE PLAN

39:12.558 --> 39:14.769
TO DECLARE BANKRUPTCY

39:12.558 --> 39:14.769
AND NOT PAY ANYONE.

39:14.769 --> 39:18.315
OR IT COULD HAVE BEEN THE MATTER

39:14.769 --> 39:18.315
OF YOU PUTTING A BOUNTY

39:18.315 --> 39:21.860
ON THE HEAD OF SOMEBODY

39:18.315 --> 39:21.860
THAT THEY COUNT ON.

39:21.860 --> 39:24.196
WHO ARE YOU GUYS?

39:24.196 --> 39:25.780
ENFORCERS ARE PUT ON THE ICE

39:25.780 --> 39:27.615
TO MAKE SURE

39:25.780 --> 39:27.615
THINGS DON'T GO TOO FAR.

39:27.615 --> 39:31.119
IF THEY DO,

39:27.615 --> 39:31.119
THEY STEP IN -- REGULATE.

39:31.119 --> 39:35.456
EVERY PLAYER ON THIS ICE

39:31.119 --> 39:35.456
IS AN ENFORCER.

39:36.708 --> 39:39.377
THERE'S NO REASON TO DO THIS.

39:39.377 --> 39:41.420
OH, THERE'S EVERY REASON

39:39.377 --> 39:41.420
TO DO THIS.

39:41.420 --> 39:42.964
WHAT DO YOU WANT, HUH?!

39:42.964 --> 39:44.841
I GOT NOTHING!

39:44.841 --> 39:46.509
THEY TOOK EVERYTHING!

39:46.509 --> 39:49.846
NOPE.

39:46.509 --> 39:49.846
NOT EVERYTHING.

39:52.849 --> 39:54.851
THE TEAM.

39:54.851 --> 39:57.020
YES.

39:57.020 --> 39:59.564
THIS IS THE CONTRACT

39:57.020 --> 39:59.564
FOR THE SALE OF THE TEAM.

39:59.564 --> 40:03.151
YOU DID ALL THIS SO THAT

39:59.564 --> 40:03.151
YOU COULD OWN THE OTTERS?

40:03.151 --> 40:05.237
I'M NOT GONNA BE

40:03.151 --> 40:05.237
THE NEW OWNER OF THE OTTERS.

40:05.237 --> 40:07.864
NO. THEY WILL.

40:31.554 --> 40:34.015
UGH!

40:47.320 --> 40:49.488
THANK YOU.

40:50.489 --> 40:52.742
I'M NOT GONNA

40:50.489 --> 40:52.742
FORGET ABOUT THIS, MARKO.

40:52.742 --> 40:55.036
GOOD...JACQUES.

41:06.631 --> 41:07.757
[ WHISTLE BLOWS ]

41:07.757 --> 41:10.718
ALL RIGHT, GUYS!

41:07.757 --> 41:10.718
LET'S DO IT AGAIN!

41:10.718 --> 41:13.012
YOU SAID YOU WANT TO BE

41:10.718 --> 41:13.012
A PART OF THIS?

41:13.012 --> 41:14.722
COME ON, LITTLE MARKO!

41:14.722 --> 41:18.226
SO, IS IT SOMEPLACE WARM?

41:18.226 --> 41:19.477
I DON'T REMEMBER.

41:19.477 --> 41:20.853
HMM.

41:21.813 --> 41:23.106
IS IT IN BOSTON?

41:23.106 --> 41:25.233
NATE, I DON'T REMEMBER.

41:25.233 --> 41:26.985
ARE YOU SURE

41:25.233 --> 41:26.985
IT'S THE STANLEY CUP?

41:26.985 --> 41:29.112
THAT I REMEMBER.

41:29.112 --> 41:32.449
WHERE'S THE LAST PLACE

41:29.112 --> 41:32.449
YOU REMEMBER, UH, HAVING IT?

41:33.658 --> 41:35.368
I DON'T REMEMBER.

